    <Paragraph>This page contains links to documents that discuss how to implement interoperation between Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) applications and other types of Microsoft Windows applications. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph FontSize="22">In This Section
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph><Run>Migration and Interoperability Overviews </Run>
<Span><Run>Topics that provide conceptual details on Windows Forms and WPF interoperation.</Run>
</Span>

